往莫斯科，波音飞机也于今年 3 月 4 日从迪拜飞往莫斯科，这三次飞行均没有获得美国方面的相关许可证。路透社报道称，除了扣押飞机，美国司法部可能会对阿布拉莫维奇的无证飞行进行罚款，三次总计罚款可能将达到近 100 万美元，约合人民币 665 万元。价值超 27 亿元！俄富翁两架豪华飞机遭美国扣押：一架波音 787 梦幻客机，一架湾流 G650 ER"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-34b6f5c4c3a7fcb7052c2aea8ffd3d6f.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "227 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/536525564"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ipu6R8PWvq7JKEAMaCDgxNTA5NTU0IPOz/JQGMAo4oAFADHIJNTM2NTI1NTY0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1654841485.0585153", "card_id": "Q_536718618", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 134}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待刘宇宁在直播中称「古装戏不需要太多演技」？为什么古装剧比现代剧更容易入门和出圈？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "古装戏不需要太多演技，及格够用就可以了！古装剧的颜值和人设才是最重要的，这两点拿捏住这个戏就差不多了。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-d7a563afde8a5517b8b7a6d7b826fa89_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "182 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/536718618"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ipu6R8PWvq7JKEAMaCDgxNTUyNTUwIIahgpUGMBI4zwFADXIJNTM2NzE4NjE4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1654841485.05948", "card_id": "Q_532826121", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 139}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么高考后会有那么多人去学驾照？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "必须要学吗，不学的话有什么不利的影响吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-331fd29ed04c1ac13d1ff9bbdb349430_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "155 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/532826121"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIp